channel.title: How do I join a different server other that HybridScape?
channel.description:
Hi, I am useing the webclient of MoparScape 3.1, but all I can connect to is HybridScape. I know if you go to >File>New Server and type in the IP Address it changes the server, but when I try to login, it tells me "Error connecting to server. Click "cancel" then "start server" to make your own."
I'm guessing this is easy to fix and I'm just not getting it. Can anyone help me with this?
